{
  "video_id": "Ue8G_TT1cZY",
  "title": "Basic income: utopia or solution? | Guy Standing | TEDxLakeComo",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Michele Gianella Reviewer: Ellen Maloney"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14880.0,
      "end_time": 19140.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very difficult to follow a fantastic musician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19840.0,
      "end_time": 23360.0,
      "text": "and then a beautiful woman with a baby robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23362.0,
      "end_time": 26919.0,
      "text": "Very difficult, especially as you&#39;re all looking forward to lunch."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27600.0,
      "end_time": 29440.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30600.0,
      "end_time": 36400.0,
      "text": "And I want to take up the theme of this wonderful [TEDxLakeComo]"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 37000.0,
      "end_time": 39430.0,
      "text": "by talking about bridges."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39880.0,
      "end_time": 45200.0,
      "text": "The first bridge I want to mention is that 800 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 46560.0,
      "end_time": 50680.0,
      "text": "a 10-year-old king, who didn&#39;t know what he was doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 52400.0,
      "end_time": 54200.0,
      "text": "he agreed to a document"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 55440.0,
      "end_time": 60760.0,
      "text": "which guaranteed every man and woman in society"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 62000.0,
      "end_time": 64280.0,
      "text": "a right to subsistence."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 64920.0,
      "end_time": 67320.0,
      "text": "A right, in effect, to a basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 68280.0,
      "end_time": 72160.0,
      "text": "A right to a home, a right to work and live in the Commons."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 73440.0,
      "end_time": 79399.0,
      "text": "He spent the next 50 years of his reign trying to reform that."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 80560.0,
      "end_time": 82280.0,
      "text": "But he was wisely told"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 83200.0,
      "end_time": 85840.0,
      "text": "that if he tried, there would be a revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 86640.0,
      "end_time": 91880.0,
      "text": "because the people wanted to keep the right to a basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 93200.0,
      "end_time": 95480.0,
      "text": "And I want to trace that history"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 96280.0,
      "end_time": 101920.0,
      "text": "as a bridge from 800 years ago to when I was a student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 103800.0,
      "end_time": 108840.0,
      "text": "and I came to believe that the only progressive policy to come"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 108840.0,
      "end_time": 113360.0,
      "text": "in response to the neoliberal economics that we were seeing develop"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 114520.0,
      "end_time": 116509.0,
      "text": "would be a basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 117560.0,
      "end_time": 122760.0,
      "text": "Let me first define it, and then talk about the second bridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 123400.0,
      "end_time": 125350.0,
      "text": "A basic income would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 125350.0,
      "end_time": 129638.0,
      "text": "if everyone of us in this room, and the children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 130800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 135440.0,
      "text": "would have the right to a modest, regular payment from the State,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 137240.0,
      "end_time": 140720.0,
      "text": "that would be unconditional in behavioural terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 141480.0,
      "end_time": 143959.0,
      "text": "paid in cash - you can do what you like with it -"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 145381.0,
      "end_time": 146680.0,
      "text": "and it would be individual."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 148920.0,
      "end_time": 149920.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what we mean by a basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 150880.0,
      "end_time": 155560.0,
      "text": "The rhetoric of the MoVimento 5 Stelle has started to change things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 155560.0,
      "end_time": 158470.0,
      "text": "but they don&#39;t quite mean the same thing as I might mean it -"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 158470.0,
      "end_time": 160600.0,
      "text": "but that, we can leave aside."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 160900.0,
      "end_time": 163900.0,
      "text": "Because the second bridge is this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 164760.0,
      "end_time": 169959.0,
      "text": "today we are on the bridge, at the beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 171600.0,
      "end_time": 174960.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;re faced by eight giants"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 176320.0,
      "end_time": 180160.0,
      "text": "that are blocking our path to a good society."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 183000.0,
      "end_time": 185440.0,
      "text": "But another metaphor that one could use"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 186680.0,
      "end_time": 189880.0,
      "text": "is that we are faced with a \"tempesta perfetta\" -"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 190640.0,
      "end_time": 193880.0,
      "text": "a Perfect Storm of factors"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 193880.0,
      "end_time": 198519.0,
      "text": "which are suddenly making the advocacy of a basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 199550.0,
      "end_time": 200560.0,
      "text": "almost mainstream."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 202000.0,
      "end_time": 204350.0,
      "text": "For many years, people like myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 204350.0,
      "end_time": 208280.0,
      "text": "were regarded as mad, bad and dangerous to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 209920.0,
      "end_time": 214559.0,
      "text": "Communist, idealist, utopian - you name it."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 216163.0,
      "end_time": 219310.0,
      "text": "A lot of rude words were thrown in our direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 219860.0,
      "end_time": 222100.0,
      "text": "But in the last five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 222100.0,
      "end_time": 226200.0,
      "text": "this perfect storm has changed the dialogue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 226200.0,
      "end_time": 228280.0,
      "text": "changed the atmosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 229400.0,
      "end_time": 233970.0,
      "text": "So suddenly we&#39;re becoming almost respectable."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 233970.0,
      "end_time": 236470.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a dangerous position to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 236960.0,
      "end_time": 239880.0,
      "text": "So one gets invited to TEDxTalks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 240720.0,
      "end_time": 244720.0,
      "text": "when before one would&#39;ve been regarded as too mad to invite."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 247280.0,
      "end_time": 251200.0,
      "text": "Now, what are these giants that are standing before us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 252640.0,
      "end_time": 253959.0,
      "text": "The first giant"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 254880.0,
      "end_time": 259988.0,
      "text": "is that we are faced by incredible inequality."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 260978.0,
      "end_time": 262460.0,
      "text": "Globalisation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 262460.0,
      "end_time": 266419.0,
      "text": "and the technological changes, and the political changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 266420.0,
      "end_time": 270920.0,
      "text": "have resulted in a terrible model of capitalism"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 270920.0,
      "end_time": 272560.0,
      "text": "in which a tiny plutocracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 272560.0,
      "end_time": 276440.0,
      "text": "is absorbing and taking billions out of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 277600.0,
      "end_time": 279720.0,
      "text": "leaving the rest of us to squabble"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 280440.0,
      "end_time": 283880.0,
      "text": "over a diminishing amount of income."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 285205.0,
      "end_time": 286599.0,
      "text": "This is a cause of migration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 286600.0,
      "end_time": 290520.0,
      "text": "this is a cause of all the other things I&#39;m going to talk about."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 290520.0,
      "end_time": 295200.0,
      "text": "So your plutocrats up here are making billions."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 296680.0,
      "end_time": 299160.0,
      "text": "One of my favorites is Jeff Bezos."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 300530.0,
      "end_time": 302119.0,
      "text": "Jeff Bezos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 303120.0,
      "end_time": 305480.0,
      "text": "each week of this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 306270.0,
      "end_time": 307280.0,
      "text": "each week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 308320.0,
      "end_time": 313400.0,
      "text": "he has increased his income by 400 million dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 314560.0,
      "end_time": 318640.0,
      "text": "I haven&#39;t made 400 million dollar in the past six months!"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 320315.0,
      "end_time": 322480.0,
      "text": "And I dare to say, most of you are like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 323580.0,
      "end_time": 324719.0,
      "text": "Every week!"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 326400.0,
      "end_time": 330840.0,
      "text": "Now, these plutocrats, of course, are striding the Globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 331520.0,
      "end_time": 334479.0,
      "text": "One of their people is in the White House,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 334480.0,
      "end_time": 336680.0,
      "text": "and many others are in positions of power."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 338920.0,
      "end_time": 340200.0,
      "text": "The real message of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 340200.0,
      "end_time": 345240.0,
      "text": "is that the income distribution system of the 20th century has broken down."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 346320.0,
      "end_time": 347840.0,
      "text": "It used to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 347840.0,
      "end_time": 349880.0,
      "text": "that when you had a capitalist economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 349880.0,
      "end_time": 353480.0,
      "text": "the share of income going to profits from capital and rents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 353910.0,
      "end_time": 355440.0,
      "text": "and the share going to labour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 355440.0,
      "end_time": 356858.0,
      "text": "were roughly constant."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 357800.0,
      "end_time": 360400.0,
      "text": "But in the last 30 years all over the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 360400.0,
      "end_time": 364248.0,
      "text": "the share going to capital is going up, the share going to labour has gone down."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 365850.0,
      "end_time": 366239.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t need to tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 366240.0,
      "end_time": 369360.0,
      "text": "that our wages have been stagnating in real terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 369360.0,
      "end_time": 370720.0,
      "text": "becoming more volatile."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 372480.0,
      "end_time": 375320.0,
      "text": "This story of inequality is unsustainable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 376560.0,
      "end_time": 379840.0,
      "text": "because there is nothing out there which is reversing this trend."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 381720.0,
      "end_time": 387880.0,
      "text": "The second giant goes along with it: it&#39;s about chronic insecurity."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 389240.0,
      "end_time": 394120.0,
      "text": "Millions of people out there, and I dare say in here as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 395240.0,
      "end_time": 397920.0,
      "text": "are suffering from chronic insecurity."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 399400.0,
      "end_time": 403160.0,
      "text": "Their lives are defined by a feeling of uncertainty."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 403840.0,
      "end_time": 405400.0,
      "text": "Unknown unknowns."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 406920.0,
      "end_time": 410600.0,
      "text": "And this insecurity cannot be insured against."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 410600.0,
      "end_time": 416560.0,
      "text": "The shocks and the hazards go on, and it leads to what I call the four As."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 417960.0,
      "end_time": 419200.0,
      "text": "A sense of anxiety."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 420640.0,
      "end_time": 425240.0,
      "text": "A sense of anomy, desperate feelings you can&#39;t do anything about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 425920.0,
      "end_time": 430640.0,
      "text": "A sense of alienation: I feel alienated from what I&#39;m doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 432200.0,
      "end_time": 434159.0,
      "text": "And a sense of anger!"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 435310.0,
      "end_time": 439000.0,
      "text": "Anger out there is justifiable."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 440920.0,
      "end_time": 443800.0,
      "text": "And this leads to the third giant."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 444640.0,
      "end_time": 448120.0,
      "text": "We have a pandemic of stress."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 449640.0,
      "end_time": 451880.0,
      "text": "People feel stressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 451880.0,
      "end_time": 455920.0,
      "text": "they feel that they don&#39;t have any sense of control of their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 456840.0,
      "end_time": 458501.0,
      "text": "They feel they don&#39;t know"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 458502.0,
      "end_time": 460640.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s the best thing to do with their time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 460640.0,
      "end_time": 462630.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re part of the precariat"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 462630.0,
      "end_time": 464159.0,
      "text": "or could be part of the precariat tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 465320.0,
      "end_time": 470840.0,
      "text": "And this stress has led to morbidity, to more suicidal tendencies."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 472640.0,
      "end_time": 479560.0,
      "text": "To an incredible phenomenon: life expectancy, in many countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 479560.0,
      "end_time": 483280.0,
      "text": "has stopped going up, and started to come down!"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 484370.0,
      "end_time": 488940.0,
      "text": "So even middle-aged people, like many of you in this room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 488940.0,
      "end_time": 492560.0,
      "text": "have suddenly found that you&#39;re suffering from morbidity."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 494680.0,
      "end_time": 498400.0,
      "text": "And it goes with the next giant:"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 500800.0,
      "end_time": 501960.0,
      "text": "a sense of precarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 503440.0,
      "end_time": 507330.0,
      "text": "My books on the precariat have somehow changed my life as well"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 507330.0,
      "end_time": 511919.0,
      "text": "as led to me receiving thousands and thousands of emails"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 511920.0,
      "end_time": 515320.0,
      "text": "from people who say they are part of the precariat."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 516240.0,
      "end_time": 518909.0,
      "text": "And they understand, and no one&#39;s listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 521159.0,
      "end_time": 523880.0,
      "text": "And what does it really mean to be part of the precariat?"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 525800.0,
      "end_time": 531319.0,
      "text": "It really means, as the Old Latin for \"precarious\" said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 532160.0,
      "end_time": 534400.0,
      "text": "you have to obtain everything by prayer."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 535640.0,
      "end_time": 537319.0,
      "text": "You are a supplicant."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 537320.0,
      "end_time": 540800.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t have a sense of agency."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 540800.0,
      "end_time": 543800.0,
      "text": "You have a sense that you have to ask for favours."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 543800.0,
      "end_time": 545640.0,
      "text": "You have to be nice to people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 545660.0,
      "end_time": 547719.0,
      "text": "not because you want to be nice"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 547720.0,
      "end_time": 551000.0,
      "text": "but because that is the way that you get some favours done."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 553120.0,
      "end_time": 556320.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an undignified type of existence"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 556320.0,
      "end_time": 560600.0,
      "text": "which many of our fellow citizens are experiencing right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 563240.0,
      "end_time": 567160.0,
      "text": "Then it&#39;s something that leads to a feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 568480.0,
      "end_time": 571480.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;re running on sinking sand."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 572960.0,
      "end_time": 575290.0,
      "text": "Running on sinking sand."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 576960.0,
      "end_time": 580560.0,
      "text": "And that leads to the next giant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 582280.0,
      "end_time": 584790.0,
      "text": "which goes with all the other things"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 584800.0,
      "end_time": 587800.0,
      "text": "but if you&#39;re in the precariat you face it every single day."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 588400.0,
      "end_time": 589810.0,
      "text": "You are in debt."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 590480.0,
      "end_time": 593680.0,
      "text": "You are living a life of indebtedness"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 594480.0,
      "end_time": 598800.0,
      "text": "where one accident, one illness, one mistake"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 599960.0,
      "end_time": 602320.0,
      "text": "could lead you to be out in the streets."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 604560.0,
      "end_time": 608439.0,
      "text": "Sometimes I use the term \"The bag lady syndrome\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 609465.0,
      "end_time": 612400.0,
      "text": "People waking up in the middle of the night with a nightmare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 612920.0,
      "end_time": 616640.0,
      "text": "thinking that one error and they&#39;re out in the streets"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 616640.0,
      "end_time": 619319.0,
      "text": "with all their belongings in two paper bags."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 620960.0,
      "end_time": 624280.0,
      "text": "If you haven&#39;t seen anybody like that, you&#39;re blind."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 624960.0,
      "end_time": 626200.0,
      "text": "Everywhere we see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 627720.0,
      "end_time": 631235.0,
      "text": "And that sense of debt"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 632735.0,
      "end_time": 637800.0,
      "text": "goes with the last two giants out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 639200.0,
      "end_time": 640480.0,
      "text": "The first one"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 640480.0,
      "end_time": 643680.0,
      "text": "is the one that should worry every single one of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 643680.0,
      "end_time": 645290.0,
      "text": "every single day."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 646400.0,
      "end_time": 648720.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the threat of extinction."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 650000.0,
      "end_time": 653560.0,
      "text": "The threats that our species are disappearing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 653560.0,
      "end_time": 656880.0,
      "text": "the threat that global warming is rushing towards us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 656880.0,
      "end_time": 660160.0,
      "text": "the threat that the pollution is meaning toxic air"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 660160.0,
      "end_time": 665790.0,
      "text": "for our children to be breathing and shortening their life expectancy."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 665940.0,
      "end_time": 668210.0,
      "text": "And it goes with many of the other things"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 668210.0,
      "end_time": 672560.0,
      "text": "because we have an agenda of economic growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 673920.0,
      "end_time": 676319.0,
      "text": "at a time of depleted resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 677800.0,
      "end_time": 682400.0,
      "text": "and at a time when we shouldn&#39;t be trying to chase faster and faster growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 683280.0,
      "end_time": 686600.0,
      "text": "But you have to chase fast growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 686600.0,
      "end_time": 691720.0,
      "text": "if most of the returns to growth go to the plutocrats on the Ã©lite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 692420.0,
      "end_time": 695790.0,
      "text": "and the people down the bottom are not benefiting."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 695852.0,
      "end_time": 697439.0,
      "text": "So you have to have faster growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 697440.0,
      "end_time": 699880.0,
      "text": "in order to raise living standards down here."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 701800.0,
      "end_time": 706280.0,
      "text": "And therefore the politicians use the rhetoric of growth:"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 706280.0,
      "end_time": 707880.0,
      "text": "\"We&#39;ve got to accelerate growth!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 709200.0,
      "end_time": 713520.0,
      "text": "At a time when we should be listening and thinking ecologically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 714106.0,
      "end_time": 716560.0,
      "text": "to reorient and recalibrate"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 717365.0,
      "end_time": 719175.0,
      "text": "what we mean by growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 721105.0,
      "end_time": 724570.0,
      "text": "Now, all of these things, these first giants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 724570.0,
      "end_time": 727880.0,
      "text": "can be addressed by giving people basic security."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 729480.0,
      "end_time": 733720.0,
      "text": "If you have basic security, a modest basic income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 735000.0,
      "end_time": 736640.0,
      "text": "your life is less insecure."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 737960.0,
      "end_time": 740160.0,
      "text": "You can reduce the inequalities."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 740920.0,
      "end_time": 744920.0,
      "text": "You can encourage people to spend more time"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 744920.0,
      "end_time": 748839.0,
      "text": "in activities like care, like voluntary work."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 749520.0,
      "end_time": 752400.0,
      "text": "Like doing the things that we all want to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 753560.0,
      "end_time": 756119.0,
      "text": "instead of chasing the next Euro"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 756120.0,
      "end_time": 761240.0,
      "text": "and following a doctrine of jobs, jobs, jobs, jobs, jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 763800.0,
      "end_time": 765560.0,
      "text": "Many forms of work don&#39;t count as jobs!"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 766880.0,
      "end_time": 768640.0,
      "text": "The economists have misled us."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 769760.0,
      "end_time": 773560.0,
      "text": "If I care for my elderly mother, that&#39;s not working."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 774520.0,
      "end_time": 778000.0,
      "text": "If I care for your elderly mother, and you pay me a wage, it&#39;s working."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 779600.0,
      "end_time": 781400.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s sexist and stupid."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 782640.0,
      "end_time": 787000.0,
      "text": "But we need to face the reality"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 787000.0,
      "end_time": 790320.0,
      "text": "that we need to have a basic income for a good society."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 790320.0,
      "end_time": 794520.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not a panacea, but it&#39;s an essential attribute."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 795880.0,
      "end_time": 797640.0,
      "text": "But what is the eighth giant?"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 798880.0,
      "end_time": 802520.0,
      "text": "The eighth giant is coming up at the other side of the bridge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 804230.0,
      "end_time": 806800.0,
      "text": "and it should be scaring us."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 808240.0,
      "end_time": 812380.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the giant of neo-fascism."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 813690.0,
      "end_time": 815490.0,
      "text": "Of authoritarianism."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 816480.0,
      "end_time": 822600.0,
      "text": "An alliance between the plutocrats and the atavistic part of the precariat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 823200.0,
      "end_time": 827276.0,
      "text": "who listen to the sirens of neofascists"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 827276.0,
      "end_time": 830640.0,
      "text": "who say, the enemy is the other!"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 831640.0,
      "end_time": 836310.0,
      "text": "The enemy is not you, it&#39;s not me, it&#39;s the other!"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 838000.0,
      "end_time": 843480.0,
      "text": "We are seeing something that I thought we would never see in my lifetime:"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 845120.0,
      "end_time": 847000.0,
      "text": "a revival of a rhetoric,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 848680.0,
      "end_time": 854400.0,
      "text": "a revival of a set of images that go back to the 1930s."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 856120.0,
      "end_time": 860960.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re seeing authoritarian, panopticon developments."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 862480.0,
      "end_time": 865400.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s this that I think [is] this giant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 866200.0,
      "end_time": 869280.0,
      "text": "that is now suddenly making a lot of corporate people -"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 870320.0,
      "end_time": 873000.0,
      "text": "a lot of people in the centre of politics"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 873960.0,
      "end_time": 877460.0,
      "text": "suddenly say, we must do something."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 879520.0,
      "end_time": 881609.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t know what,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 881609.0,
      "end_time": 884840.0,
      "text": "but they are more open to this dialogue."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 884840.0,
      "end_time": 888800.0,
      "text": "We need a gentle society, we need a convivial society."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 888880.0,
      "end_time": 890490.0,
      "text": "We need to slow down!"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 891160.0,
      "end_time": 894400.0,
      "text": "We need to rescue control on our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 894920.0,
      "end_time": 896479.0,
      "text": "Recreate solidarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 898760.0,
      "end_time": 902840.0,
      "text": "And I think the precariat, the progressive part of the precariat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 902840.0,
      "end_time": 904920.0,
      "text": "in Italy and everywhere else"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 906000.0,
      "end_time": 910557.0,
      "text": "understands the existential threats"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 910557.0,
      "end_time": 913400.0,
      "text": "of this model of global capitalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 914560.0,
      "end_time": 918479.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m eking out, waiting, looking for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 918480.0,
      "end_time": 922200.0,
      "text": "trying to create a new politics of Paradise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 922200.0,
      "end_time": 923970.0,
      "text": "with apologies to Dante."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 925280.0,
      "end_time": 928290.0,
      "text": "To escape from the politics of Inferno,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 928945.0,
      "end_time": 931205.0,
      "text": "which is rushing towards us."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 933120.0,
      "end_time": 935240.0,
      "text": "I believe there&#39;s a new generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 935240.0,
      "end_time": 938880.0,
      "text": "of politics, of politicians, of political movements."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 939760.0,
      "end_time": 941960.0,
      "text": "Many of us in this room would think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 941960.0,
      "end_time": 945920.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re not such good people, not such good messages bla, bla, bla -"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 947400.0,
      "end_time": 948920.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;re creating the space."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 949920.0,
      "end_time": 951560.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re creating a new energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 952720.0,
      "end_time": 955480.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re asking the right questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 956400.0,
      "end_time": 960199.0,
      "text": "That is why I welcome these new forms of politics."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 961920.0,
      "end_time": 964959.0,
      "text": "And I think, all of us have a job."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 966960.0,
      "end_time": 969590.0,
      "text": "Politicians, by their nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 970670.0,
      "end_time": 973349.0,
      "text": "have spaghetti spines -"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 973910.0,
      "end_time": 975209.0,
      "text": "not very strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 976800.0,
      "end_time": 977200.0,
      "text": "Spaghetti spines."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 978240.0,
      "end_time": 983560.0,
      "text": "Our job is to stiffen their spines, and make them bold."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 984400.0,
      "end_time": 986600.0,
      "text": "Make them feel that they are the leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 986600.0,
      "end_time": 992560.0,
      "text": "they are creating and establishing a new convivial good society."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 994320.0,
      "end_time": 998800.0,
      "text": "And that is why I hope some of you in this room will join us"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 999000.0,
      "end_time": 1003920.0,
      "text": "in fighting for a basic income as part of a new distribution system."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 1004550.0,
      "end_time": 1006430.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 1006430.0,
      "end_time": 1008863.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}